body: ### [Gianna Drake-Kerrison](https://joeycl1.github.io/Profile/) A portfolio page for UBS's financial advisor, Gianna Drake. The site is build as a way to introduce Gianna to her prospects and clients. In the site, it gives a brief background, value and works that she does for her client. At the same time, the site provide ways to contact Gianna. ### CIL A website template for online shopping ### Birthday Card A special birthday card template for a special individual.Alternative way to congratulate someone on his or her special day with a webpage dedicated to him or her. ### [Sample Front Page](https://joeycl1.github.io/Sample/) A sample front page that can be used for various purpose.
